<item>
            <title>[LU-6782] conf-sanity test_0: memory leaks detected</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6782</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah_lw &amp;lt;wei3.liu@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/e49aea9c-123c-11e5-89c4-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/e49aea9c-123c-11e5-89c4-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_0 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;cleanup failed with 203
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Not sure if this is a dup of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6485&quot; title=&quot;sanity-hsm test 500 memory leak&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-6485&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-6485&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;CMD: shadow-46vm6.shadow.whamcloud.com lsmod | grep lnet &amp;gt; /dev/null &amp;amp;&amp;amp; lctl dl | grep &apos; ST &apos;
LustreError: 5628:0:(class_obd.c:680:cleanup_obdclass()) obd_memory max: 182523438, leaked: 48

Memory leaks detected
 conf-sanity test_0: @@@@@@ FAIL: cleanup failed with 203 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
